import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
def load_data(fname):
    with open(fname, 'rb') as outfile:
        data_dict = pickle.load(outfile)
    return data_dict
def save_data(data_dict,fname):
    with open(fname,'wb') as outfile:
        pickle.dump(data_dict,outfile)
